{"tid":1738590,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請大家令到身邊藍絲都屌鳩政府 覺得政府係垃圾","createTime":"2019-11-19T09:43:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T08:45:55.000Z","uid":92,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"514b5a0993ae9f4d34bc4f5eeca4e774be84ef0e","tid":1738590,"uid":92,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T09:43:03.000Z","msg":"如果大家呢個時間仲想班藍絲了解整場運動背後理念呢，就請慳返啖氣。除非你可以令佢地受毛漢咁既震撼教育。<br />\n<br />\n眼見班上左年紀既藍絲，依然覺得政府同警察係權威，所以佢地做咩都啱。<br />\n<br />\n入正題，首先大家要集中屌政府所謂既「止暴制亂」，結果就係愈搞愈亂，順勢要屌埋班狗辦事不力，最好就講埋ot十幾萬人工，tg 500蚊粒等，洗咁多錢，結果咩到做唔到，愈搞愈衰。等班自私撚知係政府既問題。<br />\n<br />\n其次就係公共設施被破壞後既復原同維修，亦要屌政府唔做野，好似我屋企附近有個紅綠燈被噴黑，幾個月都冇人整。呢個時候佢地就一定會講「暴徒唔出黎搞事咪無事囉」，咁請你馬上荷蘭叻上身講「呢d唔關我事，唔通要我落場捉人咩，依家現實情況就係政府廢，咩都做唔到」。請大家善用「我唔識！我唔信！我睇唔到！唔關我 事！」，將話題帶返去屌政府。<br />\n<br />\n最終目的就係要佢地認清政府同警察唔係權威，因為個政府廢，先會引致一連串影響到佢地既事。"},{"pid":"69f4d2283662ccf82715b6b6cef394f4d3aaf162","tid":1738590,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T09:43:46.000Z","msg":"如果聽日放棄黎明行動，變相向中共鎮壓臣服！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1738567\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1738567</a>"},{"pid":"607699865a255ac48e279af0b0e880416e0d0849","tid":1738590,"uid":81478,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T09:46:23.000Z","msg":"完美示範咩叫<br />\n人無恥 則無敵"},{"pid":"58a8115c186ecfafe41ab95d71c9b7da9eea1d4b","tid":1738590,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T09:48:26.000Z","msg":"如果可以令佢地屌柒黑警就好"},{"pid":"04883003711a27b490cc22f021e99d6e547e903c","tid":1738590,"uid":3177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T09:49:08.000Z","msg":"邊啲？<br />\n網上好多網軍"},{"pid":"d03a94ca3dfcc575b3d0fb8bf04e1535c0bfe99a","tid":1738590,"uid":21920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T09:49:19.000Z","msg":"首要事情<br />\n要令到D藍絲個腦運轉返先"},{"pid":"125420c5b5e36defa877c3742f9556de68dc4356","tid":1738590,"uid":21920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T09:49:49.000Z","msg":"佢地冇獨立思考"},{"pid":"bcdc130cbacb69f1fd6f7f9bb03359183c37439c","tid":1738590,"uid":247798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T09:52:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5093b6255fbe1d5f7bd666da8a1e4c58374704bb","tid":1738590,"uid":38317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T09:53:59.000Z","msg":"家中藍絲已經屌緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3492d95f6591dd4e7a8c7129bed79ac6463c1251","tid":1738590,"uid":335348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T09:54:39.000Z","msg":"Push<br />\n<br />\n另外，一番肺腑連同深度分析，大家都可以睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1738105/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1738105/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"e50ea985b77801b5d810aa94ef9e15e1492695bb","tid":1738590,"uid":92,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04883003711a27b490cc22f021e99d6e547e903c","tid":1738590,"uid":3177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T09:49:08.000Z","msg":"邊啲？<br />\n網上好多網軍"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T09:55:12.000Z","msg":"同五毛講係無意義<br />\n所以應該同父母，親戚朋友/任何你溝通到既人"},{"pid":"e10354dd77cc3ded4d8e20f89a7a0dedd5e80202","tid":1738590,"uid":96182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T09:59:10.000Z","msg":"事實真係好多開始屌<br />\n近排聽到某d裝修工人話d狗同政府垃撚圾<br />\n雖然最後不忘吹奏自己補返句話&quot;比著我去就打撚柒班黑衣人啦&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9d0c113fbe038c088d38bdf7dfce3c07aee4ffd","tid":1738590,"uid":288154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T08:38:35.000Z","msg":"facebook行動 ＋ 區選前幫黃藍經濟圈收料<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1741135\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1741135</a>"},{"pid":